<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <style>
      .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; }
      .header { background: #28a745; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
      .content { padding: 30px 20px; }
      .button { background: #007bff; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; margin: 20px 0; font-weight: bold; }
      .footer { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; text-align: center; color: #6c757d; }
      .highlight { background: #e3f2fd; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; border-left: 4px solid #2196f3; margin: 20px 0; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>✉️ Please Confirm Your Email</h1>
      </div>
      
      <div class="content">
        <h2>Welcome <%= @email %>!</h2>
        
        <p>Thank you for signing up with Stock Trader App! To complete your registration, please confirm your email address.</p>
        
        <div class="highlight">
          <p><strong>🔐 Email Confirmation Required</strong></p>
          <p>Click the button below to verify your email address and activate your account:</p>
        </div>
        
        <div style="text-align: center;">
          <%= link_to 'Confirm My Email Address', confirmation_url(@resource, confirmation_token: @token), class: 'button' %>
        </div>
        
        <p><strong>What happens after confirmation?</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>✅ Your email will be verified</li>
          <li>🔓 You'll be able to log in to your account</li>
          <li>📊 Your account will be reviewed for trading approval</li>
          <li>💰 Start trading once approved by our team!</li>
        </ol>
        
        <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px;">
          <strong>Trouble with the button?</strong> Copy and paste this link into your browser:<br>
          <%= confirmation_url(@resource, confirmation_token: @token) %>
        </p>
        
        <p>If you didn't create an account with us, please ignore this email.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="footer">
        <p>© 2025 Stock Trader App. Secure trading platform.</p>
        <p style="font-size: 12px;">This email was sent to <%= @email %></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
